509
01:03:02,449 --> 01:03:05,718
<i>and further arrests are expected shortly.</i>

510
01:03:09,892 --> 01:03:12,103
(O'BRIEN SWITCHES OF TELESCREEN)

511
01:03:12,930 --> 01:03:14,633
You can?

512
01:03:14,836 --> 01:03:16,602
Yes

513
01:03:16,668 --> 01:03:19,352
We're allowed that privilege.

514
01:03:19,590 --> 01:03:23,041
Some more of this? It is called wine.

515
01:03:36,763 --> 01:03:42,631
There are thought criminals who maintain
that the Resistance is not real.

516
01:03:42,896 --> 01:03:46,810
Believe me Winston, it is very real.

517
01:03:49,126 --> 01:03:52,076
Perhaps you are not familiar
with how it operates.

518
01:03:52,101 --> 01:03:55,221
I'm attentive to the news.

519
01:03:55,246 --> 01:03:56,824
Indeed.

520
01:03:56,893 --> 01:04:00,178
Then perhaps you imagine a
huge network of conspirators,

521
01:04:00,203 --> 01:04:05,410
prepared to commit any atrocity to demoralise
and weaken the order of our society.

522
01:04:06,159 --> 01:04:09,528
The reality is infinitely more subtle.

523
01:04:10,897 --> 01:04:14,825
If Goldstein himself fell into the
hands of the Thought Police,

524
01:04:14,850 --> 01:04:18,433
he could not give them
a list of his agents.

525
01:04:18,684 --> 01:04:20,925
Such a list does not exist.

526
01:04:22,604 --> 01:04:27,182
They are not an organisation
in the sense we know.

527
01:04:27,409 --> 01:04:30,944
Nothing holds it together but an idea.

528
01:04:31,071 --> 01:04:34,819
There is no possibility of change
in their lifetime.

529
01:04:34,865 --> 01:04:40,238
In the face of the Thought Police
they cannot act collectively.

530
01:04:40,529 --> 01:04:45,605
Individually they cheat, forge, blackmail.

531
01:04:45,800 --> 01:04:51,122
Corrupt children spread
disease and prostitution,

532
01:04:51,447 --> 01:04:55,942
in the name of spreading knowledge
from generation to generation,

533
01:04:55,967 --> 01:05:00,178
until in a thousand years...

534
01:05:08,088 --> 01:05:10,579
You may find this of interest.

535
01:05:16,860 --> 01:05:18,900
Thank you.

536
01:05:26,583 --> 01:05:29,388
(O'BRIEN SWITCHES ON TELESCREEN)

537
01:05:29,413 --> 01:05:33,161
<i>A rally in Victory Square
at 21.30 hours.</i>

538
01:05:33,292 --> 01:05:36,376
<i>That is the end of the announcement.</i>

539
01:05:39,733 --> 01:05:41,389
Goodbye brother.

540
01:05:41,811 --> 01:05:43,319
Goodbye.

541
01:05:52,245 --> 01:05:55,995
<i>They have attacked an unarmed
village with rocket bombs</i>

542
01:05:56,020 --> 01:06:03,066
<i>and murdered 4,000 defenceless,
innocent and peaceful citizens of Oceania.</i>

543
01:06:04,986 --> 01:06:09,482
<i>This is no longer war.
This is cold blooded murder.</i>

544
01:06:11,492 --> 01:06:16,569
<i>Until now, the war has been
conducted with honour and bravery.</i>

545
01:06:16,705 --> 01:06:21,663
<i>With the ideals of truth and justice
in the best traditions of mankind,</i>

546
01:06:21,793 --> 01:06:23,832
<i>until this moment.</i>

547
01:06:26,468 --> 01:06:32,040
<i>Brothers and sisters the endless
catalogue of bestial atrocities</i>

548
01:06:32,136 --> 01:06:38,636
<i>which will ensue from this appalling act
must, can and will be terminated.</i>

549
01:06:41,511 --> 01:06:46,671
<i>The forces of darkness and the
treasonable maggots who collaborate</i>

550
01:06:46,940 --> 01:06:51,851
<i>must, can and will be wiped
from the face of the earth.</i>

551
01:06:52,654 --> 01:06:56,105
<i>We must crush them.
We must smash them.</i>

552
01:06:56,240 --> 01:06:58,280
<i>We must stamp them out!</i>

553
01:06:59,785 --> 01:07:03,035
<i>We the people of Oceania,</i>

554
01:07:03,163 --> 01:07:06,745
<i>and our traditional allies,
the people of Eurasia</i>

555
01:07:06,875 --> 01:07:12,117
<i>will not rest until the final victory
has been achieved.</i>

556
01:07:12,255 --> 01:07:17,249
<i>Death to the eternal enemy of Oceania.</i>

557
01:07:17,649 --> 01:07:18,949
<i>Death!</i>

558
01:07:19,540 --> 01:07:20,851
<i>Death!</i>

559
01:07:21,554 --> 01:07:22,735
<i>Death!</i>

560
01:07:22,760 --> 01:07:25,237
(CROWD CHEERING)

561
01:07:25,975 --> 01:07:28,382
Brothers and sisters,

562
01:07:28,519 --> 01:07:34,142
one week from now
in this very square.

563
01:07:34,274 --> 01:07:38,271
We shall as a
demonstration of our resolve

564
01:07:38,833 --> 01:07:44,168
and as a sure sign to those who attempt
to threaten our Party and our State.

565
01:07:44,366 --> 01:07:50,071
We shall execute publicly
the same number of Eastasian prisoners

566
01:07:50,205 --> 01:07:53,823
by hanging, drawing and quartering.

567
01:07:53,999 --> 01:07:58,524
(CROWD ROARING)

568
01:08:44,878 --> 01:08:48,496
In accordance with the
principles of Doublethink.

569
01:08:48,577 --> 01:08:54,033
It does not matter if the war is not real or
when it is, that victory is not possible.

570
01:08:54,220 --> 01:08:59,640
The war is not meant to be won.
It is meant to be continuous.

571
01:08:59,767 --> 01:09:02,008
The essential act of modern warfare

572
01:09:02,144 --> 01:09:06,473
is the destruction of the
produce of human labour.

573
01:09:06,606 --> 01:09:12,644
A hierarchical society is only possible
on the basis of poverty and ignorance.

574
01:09:12,778 --> 01:09:18,650
In principle the war effort is planned to
keep society on the brink of starvation.

575
01:09:19,326 --> 01:09:24,117
The war is waged by the ruling
group against its own subjects.

576
01:09:24,247 --> 01:09:27,746
Its object is not victory
over Eurasia or Eastasia,

577
01:09:28,918 --> 01:09:33,129
but to keep the very
structure of society intact.

578
01:09:38,407 --> 01:09:40,196
Julia.

579
01:09:40,826 --> 01:09:42,865
Are you awake?

580
01:09:59,054 --> 01:10:00,963
Julia.

581
01:10:02,158 --> 01:10:05,111
There is truth and there is untruth.

582
01:10:06,868 --> 01:10:10,781
To be in a minority of one
doesn't make you mad.

583
01:10:14,833 --> 01:10:16,873
Julia my love.

584
01:10:18,523 --> 01:10:20,563
I understand how.

585
01:10:22,009 --> 01:10:24,678
But I don't understand why.

586
01:10:47,779 --> 01:10:49,818
I'm hungry.

587
01:10:51,375 --> 01:10:53,830
Let's make some more coffee.

588
01:11:09,398 --> 01:11:11,266
(NEIGHBOUR SINGS IN BACK GARDEN)

589
