that time heals all things ♫

593
01:11:38,258 --> 01:11:44,538
♪ They say you can always forget ♫

594
01:11:45,561 --> 01:11:52,961
♪ But the smiles and the
tears across the years ♫

595
01:11:54,088 --> 01:11:58,631
♪ They twist my heartstrings...

596
01:11:59,000 --> 01:12:00,660
She's beautiful.

597
01:12:06,687 --> 01:12:10,063
She's a metre across the hips, easily.

598
01:12:10,088 --> 01:12:13,431
It's her style of beauty

599
01:12:17,444 --> 01:12:19,899
The future is hers.

600
01:12:27,607 --> 01:12:29,646
We are the dead.

601
01:12:31,376 --> 01:12:33,748
We are the dead.

602
01:12:33,894 --> 01:12:37,303
TELESCREEN: You are the dead!

603
01:12:38,002 --> 01:12:42,980
TELESCREEN: Remain exactly where you are!
Make no move until you are ordered.

604
01:12:48,422 --> 01:12:51,488
- Now they can see us.
TELESCREEN: Now we can see you.

605
01:12:51,743 --> 01:12:55,159
TELESCREEN:Clasp your
hands behind your heads.

606
01:12:55,184 --> 01:12:59,133
TELESCREEN: Stand out in the middle
of the room. Stand back to back.

607
01:12:59,158 --> 01:13:02,181
TELESCREEN: Do not
touch one another.

608
