The house is surrounded.

609
01:13:06,158 --> 01:13:09,192
TELESCREEN: The house is surrounded.

610
01:13:10,162 --> 01:13:12,118
I suppose we may as well say goodbye.

611
01:13:12,143 --> 01:13:13,988
TELESCREEN: You may as well say goodbye.

612
01:13:14,051 --> 01:13:18,178
TELESCREEN: While we're on the subject,
here comes a candle to light you to bed.

613
01:13:18,203 --> 01:13:21,786
TELESCREEN: Here comes a
chopper to chop off your head.

614
01:13:59,614 --> 01:14:02,657
(JULIA GASPS)

615
01:14:35,128 --> 01:14:37,583
Pick that up.

616
01:14:52,130 --> 01:14:54,123
The Thought Police.

617
01:15:32,602 --> 01:15:35,768
TELESCREEN: 6079 Smith!
Open your eyes!

618
01:15:45,632 --> 01:15:48,882
(CELL DOOR OPENS)

619
01:16:01,891 --> 01:16:03,931
Parsons?

620
01:16:05,714 --> 01:16:07,836
Keep away from me Smith.

621
01:16:09,903 --> 01:16:12,144
I'm an agent of Goldstein.

622
01:16:17,397 --> 01:16:19,436
I didn't know it myself.

623
01:16:21,769 --> 01:16:24,972
Thought crime is so insidious.

624
01:16:26,676 --> 01:16:28,715
It just creeps up on you.

625
01:16:36,494 --> 01:16:38,616
My daughter found it out.

626
01:16:40,221 --> 01:16:42,261
Very proud of her.

627
01:16:44,094 --> 01:16:49,052
Very grateful I've been discovered
before it's too late.

628
01:16:53,931 --> 01:16:57,216
They won't shoot me will they Smith?

629
01:16:57,560 --> 01:17:00,846
I could be very useful
in a labour camp.

630
01:17:09,753 --> 01:17:11,792
TELESCREEN: Room 101

631
01:17:14,448 --> 01:17:17,206
(CELL DOOR OPENS)

632
01:17:19,222 --> 01:17:20,632
No!

633
01:17:21,759 --> 01:17:25,590
Please! You don't have to take me there.

634
01:17:26,341 --> 01:17:30,469
Why? There's nothing I won't confess.

635
01:17:31,897 --> 01:17:33,937
Nothing.

636
01:17:34,348 --> 01:17:36,507
I've told you everything already.

637
01:17:38,257 --> 01:17:40,712
What is it you want me to know?

638
01:17:43,564 --> 01:17:45,603
Take him instead of me.

639
01:17:46,164 --> 01:17:50,078
He's the thought criminal.
It's him you want.

640
01:18:12,232 --> 01:18:14,966
(CELL DOOR CLOSES)

641
01:18:24,925 --> 01:18:27,792
(CELL DOOR OPENS)

642
01:18:40,956 --> 01:18:45,368
- They got you too?
- They got me a long time ago.

643
01:18:48,968 --> 01:18:51,506
You knew this would happen Winston.

644
01:18:51,531 --> 01:18:55,611
Don't deceive yourself.
You've always known it.

645
01:19:09,133 --> 01:19:12,375
(WINSTON WHIMPERS)

646
01:19:12,400 --> 01:19:17,358
The photos of you and the girl will
be recycled for proletarian use.

647
01:19:19,888 --> 01:19:23,349
(WINSTON WHIMPERS AGAIN)

648
01:19:55,976 --> 01:19:59,310
Do you know where you are Winston?

649
01:19:59,394 --> 01:20:02,976
I... I don't know.

650
01:20:03,105 --> 01:20:05,857
I can guess.

651
01:20:05,983 --> 01:20:08,853
In the Ministry of Love.

652
01:20:08,986 --> 01:20:11,939
Do you know how long you've been here?

653
01:20:12,072 --> 01:20:14,444
No.

654
01:20:14,574 --> 01:20:17,740
Weeks? Months?

655
01:20:18,953 --> 01:20:21,278
Do you know why you're here?

656
01:20:25,448 --> 01:20:29,923
Shall I tell you why we brought
you here? To cure you.

657
01:20:30,987 --> 01:20:32,861
To make you sane.

658
01:20:33,129 --> 01:20:35,168
Yes.

659
01:20:36,878 --> 01:20:39,912
(WINSTON IS BEING STRETCHED)

660
01:20:39,930 --> 01:20:42,385
No! No! No!

661
01:20:44,406 --> 01:20:50,623
That was 40. You can see that
the numbers on this dial run up to 100.

662
01:20:50,648 --> 01:20:53,814
Will you please remember
that I have it in my power

663
01:20:53,942 --> 01:20:59,482
to inflict pain on you at any time,
and in whatever degree I choose?

664
01:20:59,965 --> 01:21:01,340
Yes.

665
01:21:06,272 --> 01:21:09,973
You know perfectly well
what is the matter with you, Winston.

666
01:21:09,998 --> 01:21:14,161
You've known it for years though
you fought against the knowledge.

667
01:21:14,399 --> 01:21:16,771
You are mentally deranged.

668
01:21:17,178 --> 01:21:20,095
You suffer from a defective memory.

669
01:21:21,037 --> 01:21:24,536
You never tried to cure yourself
because you did not choose to.

670
01:21:24,816 --> 01:21:29,857
It was a small effort of will
which you were not ready to make.

671
01:21:30,925 --> 01:21:36,215
For example, which
power is Oceania at war with?

672
01:21:38,119 --> 01:21:40,158
Eastasia.

673
01:21:41,732 --> 01:21:44,483
Oceania is at war with Eastasia.

674
01:21:44,946 --> 01:21:46,606
Eastasia?

675
01:21:46,739 --> 01:21:48,566
Good.

676
01:21:48,871 --> 01:21:52,785
And Oceania has always been at war
with Eastasia, has it not?

677
01:21:55,394 --> 01:21:58,206
Tell me what you think you remember.

678
01:22:03,258 --> 01:22:05,297
I remember

679
01:22:06,548 --> 01:22:10,711
that until only a week
before I was arrested.

680
01:22:10,736 --> 01:22:14,567
We weren't at war with Eastasia at all.

681
01:22:14,806 --> 01:22:16,845
It was Eurasia.

682
01:22:19,174 --> 01:22:22,525
- The last four years I think.
- Another example.

683
01:22:23,588 --> 01:22:25,502
A serious delusion.

684
01:22:27,126 --> 01:22:31,037
Photographs about which
you've had hallucinations,

685
01:22:31,112 --> 01:22:34,730
which you believed
you held in your hand.

686
01:22:36,428 --> 01:22:38,468
They never existed.

687
01:22:46,501 --> 01:22:48,956
Say what you're about to say Winston.

688
01:22:49,086 --> 01:22:51,838
They exist.

689
01:22:51,863 --> 01:22:54,856
In memory.

690
01:22:55,480 --> 01:22:58,399
I remember.

691
01:22:58,486 --> 01:23:01,059
You remember.

692
01:23:01,097 --> 01:23:03,801
I do not remember.

693
01:23:03,933 --> 01:23:09,602
Only the disciplined mind
can see reality Winston.

694
01:23:10,010 --> 01:23:13,842
It needs an act of self destruction,
an effort of the will.

695
01:23:15,444 --> 01:23:17,899
Do you remember writing in your diary.

696
01:23:17,924 --> 01:23:22,550
"Freedom is the freedom to say
two plus two equals four"?

697
01:23:23,617 --> 01:23:24,945
Yes.

698
01:23:25,547 --> 01:23:28,179
How many fingers am I holding up?

699
01:23:28,540 --> 01:23:29,947
Four.

700
01:23:30,111 --> 01:23:34,773
And if the Party says there are not four
but five, then how many?

701
01:23:35,294 --> 01:23:37,333
Five?

702
01:23:39,017 --> 01:23:41,650
(WINSTON SCREAMS IN PAIN)

703
01:23:44,010 --> 01:23:46,216
No.

704
01:23:46,345 --> 01:23:48,717
That's no use. You're lying.

705
01:23:50,888 --> 01:23:53,130
How many fingers please?

706
01:23:56,438 --> 01:23:59,272
Four, what else can I say?

707
01:24:01,275 --> 01:24:06,269
Five, anything you like,
only please stop it.

708
01:24:06,294 --> 01:24:08,333
Stop the pain.

709
01:24:12,869 --> 01:24:15,407
How can I help it?

710
01:24:17,416 --> 01:24:20,998
How can I help what
I see in front of my eyes?

711
01:24:21,960 --> 01:24:24,996
Two and two makes four.

712
01:24:25,240 --> 01:24:29,901
Sometimes, Winston,
sometimes they're five.

713
01:24:30,128 --> 01:24:35,204
Sometimes they're three.
Sometimes they are all of them at once.

714
01:24:44,511 --> 01:24:51,593
Neither the past nor the present nor the
future exists in its own right Winston.

715
01:24:51,932 --> 01:24:58,301
Reality is in the human mind,
not in the individual mind.

716
01:24:58,436 --> 01:25:03,430
Which makes mistakes
and soon perishes,

717
01:25:03,813 --> 01:25:09,793
but in the mind of the Party,
which is collective and immortal.

718
01:25:13,862 --> 01:25:14,915
Again.

719
01:25:14,940 --> 01:25:15,987
No.

720
01:25:17,581 --> 01:25:21,018
(WINSTON'S GROANS IN PAIN AGAIN)

721
01:25:23,265 --> 01:25:25,340
How many fingers Winston?

722
01:25:27,977 --> 01:25:30,847
Four... Four?

723
01:25:30,980 --> 01:25:35,937
I suppose there are four
but I'm trying to see five.

724
01:25:36,860 --> 01:25:39,481
- I wish I could.
- Which do you wish?

725
01:25:40,183 --> 01:25:43,717
To persuade me that you can see 
five or really to see them?

726
01:25:44,117 --> 01:25:46,109
Really to see them.

727
01:25:48,912 --> 01:25:50,952
Again.

728
01:25:58,963 --> 01:26:01,288
How many Winston?

729
01:26:11,250 --> 01:26:12,344
I...

730
01:26:12,433 --> 01:26:14,473
I don't know...

731
01:26:15,261 --> 01:26:17,503
I don't know.

732
01:26:18,856 --> 01:26:20,895
Better.

733
01:26:38,277 --> 01:26:43,237
No one escapes Winston.
There are no martyrs here.

734
01:26:43,455 --> 01:26:46,029
All the confessions made here are true.

735
01:26:47,483 --> 01:26:51,860
We do not destroy the heretic
because he resists us.

736
01:26:51,885 --> 01:26:55,799
As long as he resists us
we never destroy him.

737
01:26:55,930 --> 01:26:59,630
We make him one of ourselves
before we kill him.

738
01:26:59,767 --> 01:27:03,349
We make his brain perfect
before we blow it out.

739
01:27:04,188 --> 01:27:11,352
And then, when there is nothing left
but sorrow and love of Big Brother,

740
01:27:11,486 --> 01:27:14,605
we shall lift you clean out of history.

741
01:27:14,929 --> 01:27:19,537
We shall turn you into gas and 
pour you into the stratosphere.

742
01:27:19,576 --> 01:27:21,901
Nothing will remain of you.

743
01:27:22,037 --> 01:27:27,872
Not a name in a register,
not a memory in a living brain.

744
01:27:28,000 --> 01:27:30,491
You will be annihilated in the past,

745
01:27:30,628 --> 01:27:33,083
as well as in the future.

746
01:27:34,298 --> 01:27:36,504
3,000

747
01:27:44,098 --> 01:27:46,553
This time it won't hurt you.

748
01:27:48,418 --> 01:27:51,538
Before we bring this session to an end,

749
01:27:51,563 --> 01:27:54,433
I want you to ask me your questions.

750
01:27:54,729 --> 01:27:57,184
I want you to clear your mind.

751
01:28:00,321 --> 01:28:02,112
Julia.

752
01:28:02,340 --> 01:28:07,761
She betrayed you Winston.
Immediately. Unreservedly.

753
01:28:07,894 --> 01:28:12,306
All her rebellion, deceit,
folly, dirty mindedness

754
01:28:12,464 --> 01:28:14,706
has been turned out of her.

755
01:28:18,123 --> 01:28:20,744
Does Big Brother exist?

756
01:28:20,968 --> 01:28:23,007
Of course.

757
01:28:24,786 --> 01:28:28,237
In the same way as me?

758
01:28:28,567 --> 01:28:30,607
You do not exist.

759
01:28:34,056 --> 01:28:39,429
You have not asked me the question
that is uppermost in your mind Winston.

760
01:28:39,454 --> 01:28:41,779
You know what is in Room 101.

761
01:28:43,350 --> 01:28:46,303
Everyone knows what's in Room 101.

762
01:28:50,401 --> 01:28:54,399
Now fix your eyes on mine.

763
01:29:11,719 --> 01:29:14,838
What country is Oceania at war with?

764
01:29:15,387 --> 01:29:17,878
I...

765
01:29:18,015 --> 01:29:20,137
I don't remember.

766
01:29:20,454 --> 01:29:24,914
Oceania is at war with East Eastasia.
Do you remember that now?

767
01:29:25,355 --> 01:29:27,394
Yes.

768
01:29:28,679 --> 01:29:31,430
How many fingers am I holding up?

769
01:29:32,925 --> 01:29:34,206
Five.

770
01:29:34,888 --> 01:29:38,838
You see at least that it is possible.

771
01:29:42,391 --> 01:29:48,292
You've understood the reality of the
past and the present Winston.

772
01:29:49,112 --> 01:29:51,151
Now what of the future?

773
01:29:52,628 --> 01:29:54,035
Question.

774
01:29:55,370 --> 01:30:00,290
How does one man
assert power over another?

775
01:30:00,511 --> 01:30:04,294
- By making him suffer.
- Exactly.

776
01:30:04,431 --> 01:30:07,301
Obedience is not enough.

777
01:30:07,434 --> 01:30:11,762
Power is inflicting pain and humiliation
otherwise you cannot be sure.

778
01:30:12,205 --> 01:30:16,617
Power is tearing human minds apart

779
01:30:16,652 --> 01:30:21,112
and putting them together again
in new shapes of your own choosing.

780
01:30:21,245 --> 01:30:24,448
Power is not a means, it is an end.

781
01:30:24,675 --> 01:30:30,031
In our world there will only be triumph
and self-abasement.

782
01:30:30,056 --> 01:30:33,056
Everything else we shall destroy.

783
01:30:33,423 --> 01:30:35,353
The past is forbidden.

784
01:30:35,378 --> 01:30:36,829
Why.

785
01:30:37,273 --> 01:30:40,891
Because when we can cut 
man from his own past,

786
01:30:41,143 --> 01:30:45,492
then we can cut him from his family.
His children, other men.

787
01:30:47,864 --> 01:30:52,407
There is no loyalty
except loyalty to the Party.

788
01:30:52,721 --> 01:30:56,136
There is no love except 
love of Big Brother.

789
01:30:56,171 --> 01:31:00,832
All competing pleasures, we will destroy.

790
01:31:02,672 --> 01:31:08,959
If you want a vision of the future imagine
a boot stamping on a human face forever.

791
01:31:13,598 --> 01:31:15,638
Winston...

792
01:31:16,892 --> 01:31:21,269
You are thinking that 
my face is old and tired.

793
01:31:21,294 --> 01:31:26,597
That while I talk of power I am unable
to prevent the decay of my own body.

794
01:31:28,688 --> 01:31:32,271
But the individual is only a cell Winston.

795
01:31:32,306 --> 01:31:36,599
The weariness of the cell is 
the vigour of the organism.

796
01:31:36,624 --> 01:31:38,405
You'll fail.

797
01:31:38,430 --> 01:31:40,249
Why?

798
01:31:40,285 --> 01:31:43,369
It's impossible.

799
01:31:43,745 --> 01:31:47,908
Hatred and fear have no life.

800
01:31:48,215 --> 01:31:51,418
Why is hate less vital than love?

801
01:31:51,755 --> 01:31:55,206
I don't know but somehow you'll fail.

802
01:31:56,221 --> 01:31:59,341
Something will defeat you.

803
01:31:59,366 --> 01:32:05,319
- Life will defeat you.
- We control life at all levels.

804
01:32:06,174 --> 01:32:12,344
We create human nature.
Men are infinitely malleable.

805
01:32:12,673 --> 01:32:17,733
Or perhaps you will return to your old idea
that the proletarians will arise.

806
01:32:17,758 --> 01:32:23,000
Put it out of your mind.
They are helpless animals.

807
01:32:23,243 --> 01:32:26,991
Humanity is the party.

808
01:32:27,273 --> 01:32:31,899
I don't care, in the end they'll beat you.

809
01:32:32,027 --> 01:32:36,238
Sooner or later they'll
tear you to pieces.

810
01:32:36,960 --> 01:32:39,877
On what evidence?

811
01:32:39,902 --> 01:32:41,729
Goldstein's book.

812
01:32:43,316 --> 01:32:47,693
I wrote it, or at least
I collaborated in writing it.

813
01:32:48,225 --> 01:32:52,518
No book is individually
produced as you know.

814
01:32:52,707 --> 01:32:55,280
I just believe it.

815
01:32:56,334 --> 01:32:59,251
I know you'll fail.

816
01:32:59,557 --> 01:33:06,472
There's something in this world, some 
spirit that you will never overcome.

817
01:33:07,012 --> 01:33:09,716
What is it, this principle?

818
01:33:10,512 --> 01:33:12,551
I don't know.

819
01:33:13,411 --> 01:33:16,198
The spirit of man.

820
01:33:16,410 --> 01:33:18,284
Do you consider yourself a man?

821
01:33:19,413 --> 01:33:20,658
Yes.

822
01:33:23,158 --> 01:33:26,242
If you're a man, you're the last man.

823
01:33:26,811 --> 01:33:31,473
Your kind is extinct.
We are the inheritors.

824
01:33:33,537 --> 01:33:36,704
Do you understand that you're alone?

825
01:33:37,745 --> 01:33:39,868
You're outside history.

826
01:33:41,227 --> 01:33:43,266
You unexist.

827
01:33:46,659 --> 01:33:48,070
Get up.

828
01:34:06,624 --> 01:34:08,664
Come here.

829
01:34:25,955 --> 01:34:30,283
Look at you, you're rotting away.

830
01:34:43,227 --> 01:34:46,263
That is the last man.

831
01:34:46,404 --> 01:34:49,358
If you're human, that is humanity.

832
01:34:51,311 --> 01:34:53,350
It won't last forever.

833
01:34:54,619 --> 01:34:58,201
You can escape from it
whenever you choose.

834
01:34:58,301 --> 01:35:00,210
Everything depends on you.

835
01:35:00,344 --> 01:35:02,383
You did it.

836
01:35:02,972 --> 01:35:05,545
You reduced me to this.

837
01:35:05,823 --> 01:35:09,951
No Winston you reduced yourself to it.

838
01:35:11,838 --> 01:35:14,293
When will you shoot me?

839
01:35:16,285 --> 01:35:18,408
It might take a long time.

840
01:35:19,586 --> 01:35:22,041
But don't give up hope.

841
01:35:22,171 --> 01:35:24,840
Everyone is cured sooner or later,

842
01:35:26,934 --> 01:35:29,670
and in the end

843
01:35:29,886 --> 01:35:32,045
we shall shoot you.

844
01:35:32,533 --> 01:35:35,617
The law of gravity is nonsense.

845
01:35:35,642 --> 01:35:37,883
No such law exists.

846
01:35:38,136 --> 01:35:43,238
If I think I float and you think
I float then it happens.

847
01:35:45,132 --> 01:35:46,588
I love you.

848
01:35:46,613 --> 01:35:48,292
You have the strength Winston.

849
01:35:48,317 --> 01:35:50,418
You have the whole party.

850
01:35:50,613 --> 01:35:52,356
You are the Party.

851
01:35:52,490 --> 01:35:54,372
You're one of us.

852
01:35:54,396 --> 01:35:55,886
One of the chosen.

853
01:35:56,308 --> 01:35:57,959
I love you.

854
01:35:58,589 --> 01:36:00,268
I love you too.

855
01:36:02,605 --> 01:36:04,385
(GUNSHOT)

856
01:36:05,501 --> 01:36:07,541
Julia.

857
01:36:09,130 --> 01:36:11,169
Julia my love.

858
01:36:12,841 --> 01:36:14,881
Julia.

859
01:36:16,595 --> 01:36:18,468
Julia!

860
01:36:20,032 --> 01:36:22,048
Julia!

861
01:36:22,120 --> 01:36:24,235
TELESCREEN: Get up

862
01:36:30,100 --> 01:36:32,139
TELESCREEN: Stand up straighter.

863
01:36:33,151 --> 01:36:35,190
TELESCREEN: Look me in the face.

864
01:36:39,216 --> 01:36:43,165
Tell me Winston and remember no lies.

865
01:36:45,227 --> 01:36:49,390
What are your true feelings
towards Big Brother?

866
01:36:49,521 --> 01:36:51,231
I hate him.

867
01:36:51,256 --> 01:36:53,568
You must love him.

868
01:36:53,755 --> 01:36:57,337
It's not enough to obey him.
You must love him.

869
01:37:00,463 --> 01:37:02,705
Room 101.

870
01:37:28,992 --> 01:37:33,155
You asked me once Winston
what was in Room 101?

871
01:37:33,396 --> 01:37:36,349
I told you that you knew already.

872
01:37:36,374 --> 01:37:38,413
Everyone knows.

873
01:37:40,559 --> 01:37:43,728
The thing that is in Room 101,

874
01:37:44,112 --> 01:37:46,781
is the worst thing in the world.

875
01:37:57,462 --> 01:38:01,162
It goes beyond fear of pain or death.

876
01:38:01,291 --> 01:38:06,631
It is unendurable and it varies
from individual to individual.

877
01:38:06,859 --> 01:38:11,402
It may be burial alive or castration.

878
01:38:11,530 --> 01:38:13,569
Or many other things.

879
01:38:18,403 --> 01:38:19,942
In your case,

880
01:38:20,230 --> 01:38:21,769
it's rats

881
01:38:22,043 --> 01:38:23,783
No!

882
01:38:25,762 --> 01:38:28,070
(RATS SQUEALING)

883
01:38:28,295 --> 01:38:33,003
- Please, what do you want me to do?
- You will do what is required of you.

884
01:38:33,672 --> 01:38:35,664
What, what?

885
01:38:35,750 --> 01:38:37,047
What.

886
01:38:37,595 --> 01:38:40,699
How can I do it if I
don't know what it is?

887
01:38:42,266 --> 01:38:45,730
In the proletarian areas
they will attack a baby

888
01:38:46,173 --> 01:38:49,956
and within five minutes
strip it to the bone.

889
01:38:49,981 --> 01:38:53,760
They also attack the sick and dying.

890
01:38:54,193 --> 01:38:59,031
They show astonishing intelligence in
knowing when a human being is helpless.

891
01:38:59,056 --> 01:39:02,275
(RATS SQUEAL AGAIN)

892
01:39:07,330 --> 01:39:09,369
Please!

893
01:39:13,877 --> 01:39:18,254
The mask fits over your
head leaving no exit.

894
01:39:18,381 --> 01:39:23,437
I press the first lever and the rats
move into the front compartment.

895
01:39:23,969 --> 01:39:28,346
I press the second and the
door of the cage will slide up.

896
01:39:28,726 --> 01:39:32,558
These starving brutes
will shoot at you like bullets.

897
01:39:32,630 --> 01:39:36,114
Have you ever seen a rat 
leap through the air?

898
01:39:36,237 --> 01:39:37,729
(RATS SQUEAL)

899
01:39:39,483 --> 01:39:43,646
They will leap onto your face
and bore straight into it.

900
01:39:44,005 --> 01:39:47,290
Sometimes they attack the eyes first.

901
01:39:48,908 --> 01:39:53,486
Sometimes they burrow through
the cheeks and devour the tongue.

902
01:39:53,608 --> 01:39:55,920
(WINSTON WHIMPERS)

903
01:39:56,405 --> 01:39:58,967
Help, help me!

904
01:39:59,584 --> 01:40:01,707
What do you want?

905
01:40:06,344 --> 01:40:08,344
Help me.

906
01:40:08,660 --> 01:40:10,660
No! No!

907
01:40:11,238 --> 01:40:14,339
(RATS SQUEAL)

908
01:40:16,808 --> 01:40:18,847
I love you.

909
01:40:20,607 --> 01:40:23,861
Do it to her, do it to Julia.

910
01:40:24,356 --> 01:40:28,650
I don't care what you do to her. Tear
her face off! do it to Julia not to me.

911
01:40:31,362 --> 01:40:33,402
Do it to Julia!

912
01:40:34,305 --> 01:40:36,344
Do it to Julia!

913
01:40:37,229 --> 01:40:39,305
Not me!

914
01:40:42,831 --> 01:40:46,698
<i>A vast military build up has
been reported in the Sahara desert.</i>

915
01:40:46,835 --> 01:40:50,618
<i>Sectors 17 and 18 of the war zone.</i>

916
01:40:50,755 --> 01:40:53,839
<i>That is the end of the announcement.</i>

917
01:41:32,547 --> 01:41:34,586
Brother.

918
01:41:42,743 --> 01:41:44,700
On the house.

919
01:41:51,954 --> 01:41:53,993
Thank you for coming.

920
01:41:57,522 --> 01:42:02,100
<i>You are warned to stand by for
an important announcement at 15.30</i>

921
01:42:02,281 --> 01:42:06,792
<i>This is news of the gravest national 
consequence concerning the war with Eurasia.</i>

922
01:42:06,947 --> 01:42:08,986
<i>15.30</i>

923
01:42:09,616 --> 01:42:12,617
I'm very worried about the African front.

924
01:42:14,743 --> 01:42:19,537
The news is disquieting in the extreme.
I've been worrying about it all day.

925
01:42:19,625 --> 01:42:21,950
It's not just a question of losing Africa.

926
01:42:22,193 --> 01:42:27,399
For the first time the territory of Oceania
itself is threatened by invasion.

927
01:42:27,712 --> 01:42:30,000
It's inconceivable.

928
01:42:37,057 --> 01:42:41,802
It must have been possible
to outflank them in some way.

929
01:42:48,184 --> 01:42:50,223
I have an instinct.

930
01:42:51,435 --> 01:42:53,262
There's bad news on the way.

931
01:42:59,061 --> 01:43:01,386
I told them all about you.

932
01:43:04,021 --> 01:43:08,018
I'm only thankful they got 
me before it was too late.

933
01:43:08,146 --> 01:43:11,396
Yes I told them about you too.

934
01:43:11,616 --> 01:43:13,655
Thought crime.

935
01:43:15,442 --> 01:43:17,984
Sex crime, all your treachery.

936
01:43:26,368 --> 01:43:28,407
I have a meeting to go to.

937
01:43:32,449 --> 01:43:34,309
We must meet again.

938
01:43:36,838 --> 01:43:38,877
Yes.

939
01:43:40,953 --> 01:43:42,992
We must meet again.

940
01:43:59,783 --> 01:44:03,650
<i>I accuse myself of the following crimes.</i>

941
01:44:04,034 --> 01:44:07,154
<i>I have seduced Party
members of both sexes.</i>

942
01:44:07,289 --> 01:44:10,574
<i>I've been to the proletarian areas.</i>

943
01:44:10,707 --> 01:44:13,743
<i>I deliberately contracted syphilis
in order to spread the disease</i>

944
01:44:13,768 --> 01:44:16,437
<i>to my wife and other Party members.</i>

945
01:44:16,562 --> 01:44:21,438
<i>Together with other agents,
I have counterfeited banknotes.</i>

946
01:44:21,567 --> 01:44:26,608
<i>Wrecked industrial machinery,
polluted the water supply</i>

947
01:44:26,910 --> 01:44:30,160
<i>and guided Eurasian rocket bombs
to targets on Airstrip One</i>

948
01:44:30,233 --> 01:44:32,984
<i>by means of coded radio signals.</i>

949
01:44:34,473 --> 01:44:38,886
<i>I stand here a victim of the
influence of Emmanuel Goldstein.</i>

950
01:44:39,269 --> 01:44:41,724
<i>Guilty on all counts.</i>

951
01:44:42,858 --> 01:44:47,119
<i>I'm glad I was caught.
I was mentally deranged.</i>

952
01:44:47,392 --> 01:44:49,431
<i>Now I am cured.</i>

953
01:44:50,176 --> 01:44:54,920
<i>I ask only for you to accept
my love of our leader.</i>

954
01:44:56,299 --> 01:45:01,091
<i>I ask only to be shot while 
my mind is still clean.</i>

955
01:45:11,029 --> 01:45:12,949
(MUSICAL INTRO ON TELESCREEN)

956
01:45:13,050 --> 01:45:14,953
<i>A glorious victory.</i>

957
01:45:15,041 --> 01:45:19,718
<i>A vast strategic manoeuvre to outflank
the Eurasian forces on the African front</i>

958
01:45:19,743 --> 01:45:21,783
<i>has been successful.</i>

959
01:45:22,323 --> 01:45:28,143
<i>Perfectly coordinated, it has resulted
in the utter rout of the Eurasian army.</i>

960
01:45:28,269 --> 01:45:31,020
<i>There have been nearly 
a million prisoners.</i>

961
01:45:31,490 --> 01:45:33,763
<i>It has been an utter rout, a complete...

962
01:45:34,176 --> 01:45:35,652
Waiter!

963
01:45:37,467 --> 01:45:42,971
<i>This immense victory brings the war
within measurable distance of its end.</i>

964
01:45:44,157 --> 01:45:46,197
Wonderful news.

965
01:46:43,379 --> 01:46:45,419
I love you.

966
01:46:50,538 --> 01:46:52,683
(THE END)

